      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i just sit there and think... if he's already there, and i'm just stuck here in this gray world, maybe it's not as bad as people make it out to be. like, if the pain is the only thing left, wouldn't it be more peaceful to just be with him? to not have to fight this every single second?",
